    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>macaroni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> macaroni</strong> for 6-7 min or until cooked with a bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>macaroni</strong> reserving 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span> [200ml]</span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and set aside until later, reserve the pot</p>",
