    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add most of the <strong>caramelised onion</strong> to the cheese sauce with the <strong>drained macaroni </strong>and stir everything together – this is your <strong>mac 'n' cheese mixture</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>mac 'n' cheese mixture</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>and sprinkle over the<strong> remaining caramelised onion</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>and <strong>remaining grated cheese</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 10-12 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>French onion-style mac 'n' cheese</strong></p>",
