    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mac 'n' cheese is cooking, combine your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and <strong>Dijon mustard </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and shred roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> to the dressing<strong> </strong>and toss – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
